        "Rosetta condition: TaxonomyValue \u2014 if taxonomyValue -> nonEnumeratedTaxonomyValue exists then taxonomySource <> TaxonomySourceEnum -> EU_EMIR_EligibleCollateralAssetClass and taxonomySource <> TaxonomySourceEnum -> UK_EMIR_EligibleCollateralAssetClass and taxonomySource <> TaxonomySourceEnum -> US_CFTC_PR_EligibleCollateralAssetClass"
      ],
