      "description": "The party specific elections in respect to the Specified Condition and Access Condition clause.",
      "comments": [
        "Rosetta condition: AdditionalTerminationEvent \u2014 if specifiedOrAccessCondition any = CSASpecifiedOrAccessConditionEnum -> AdditionalTerminationEvents then additionalTerminationEvent exists else additionalTerminationEvent is absent",
        "Rosetta condition: SpecifiedAdditionalTerminationEvent \u2014 if additionalTerminationEvent any = AdditionalTerminationEventEnum -> AsSpecified then specifiedAdditionalTerminationEvent exists else specifiedAdditionalTerminationEvent is absent"
