        "Rosetta condition: InitialStockLoanRate \u2014 if initialStockLoanRate exists then initialStockLoanRate >= 0 and initialStockLoanRate <= 1",
        "Rosetta condition: DisruptionEventsDeterminingParty \u2014 if determiningParty exists then determiningParty = AncillaryRoleEnum -> DisruptionEventsDeterminingParty"
      ],
